### 1) Search for laptops
POST http://localhost:3000/api/products/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "laptop"
}

### 2) Search for headphones
POST http://localhost:3000/api/products/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "headphones"
}

### 3) Search for coffee with location
POST http://localhost:3000/api/products/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "coffee",
  "location": {
    "country": "RO",
    "city": "Bucharest"
  }
}
